{"tid":2211264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"旺角㩒巴士緊急死火掣阻交通 官判男生社會服務令80小時","createTime":"2020-09-21T04:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T05:24:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5b963df0999ca91e48aac39bfbd8ebc2936476","tid":2211264,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9626&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=7140f44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9626</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 <br />\n#判刑 <br />\n#1211旺角 <br />\n<br />\n麥(16)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n導致交通遭受阻礙<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被控於19年12月11日，在旺角彌敦道與奶路臣街交界，無合法辯解而按下兩架新世界巴士的緊急死火掣，因而可直接造成或導致交通受阻塞<br />\n<br />\n【速報】<br />\n判處80小時社會服務令<br />\n<br />\n（詳情後補）"},{"pid":"2088fdc3089876db236e223c14b5747ec697e08b","tid":2211264,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"中五男生去年12月11日在旺角街頭按下兩輛巴士的緊急死火掣，以達致堵路效果，早前承認阻塞交通罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院判刑。辯方表示報告內容正面，父母亦到庭支持兒子。主任裁判官羅德泉最終判被告接受80小時社會服務令，並告誡謂：「社會服務令嚴重性等同坐監，唔好輕視咗佢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/XAMEBN7VJBB35G4HQJNNKHJBNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FXAMEBN7VJBB35G4HQJNNKHJBNU%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=7a4a13a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FXAMEBN7VJBB35G4HQJNNKHJBNU%2F&h=64ef0b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/XAMEBN7VJBB35G4HQJNNKHJBNU/</a>"},{"pid":"323c36a9d02f673ee5e789627a40b42f41d147d6","tid":2211264,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" cl